sample_data.question: Bitcoin above $90,000 on January 2, 5pm UTC?
sample_data.details: This market will resolve to “Yes” if the Close price of the Binance BTC/USDT 1-minute candle at 5:00 PM UTC on January 2, 2026 is above $90,000. It will resolve to “No” if the Close price at that time is below $90,000. The resolution source is Binance, using the BTC/USDT 1-minute Close price available at https://www.binance.com/en/trade/BTC_USDT with “1m” and “Candles” selected.
